snippet.title: [New Game 2023] Night-Runners Demo Progress Update!
snippet.description:
Demo will still release before the end of 2023! Patreon supporters will get early builds of the demo before full release.

Support On Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/NightRunnersGame
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/NightRunners_jp
Follow on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nightrunner...
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/night-runners

Night-Runners is a PC street racing game heavily influenced by 1990s - early 2000s car culture. Release date unannounced.

00:29 Garage w/ new car
01:31 Demo area map
02:06 Driving To Tatsumi PA via tunnels
02:58 First Person camera
04:40 Enter Tatsumi PA
05:12 Walk around Parking Area
05:42 Challenge Racer
06:38 Race Intro
07:02 Race fixing offer
